high_descs: Turn right, move to the counter left of the stove.
Pick up the knife, with the yellow handle, from the counter.
Turn left, move to the table, between the chairs.
Slice the tomato on the table.
Turn right, move to the bin at the end of the counter.
Put the knife in the bin.
Turn left, move to the table, between the chairs.
Pick up a slice of tomato from the table.
Turn right, move to in front of the refrigerator.
Put the tomato slice in the refrigerator, chill it, pick it back up.
Turn right, move to the bin at the end of the counter.
Put the tomato slice in the bin.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled slice of tomato in a bin.

high_descs: Walk forward then turn right head to the counter
Pick up the knife on the counter
Turn left head to the round table
Slice the tomato on the table
Turn right and head to the  trash bin on your left
Drop the knife in the trash bin
Turn left head to the left side of the round table
Pick up a slice of tomato
Turn around to your right face the fridge
Open the fridge put in and out the tomato
Turn right then head to the trash bin
Drop the slice tomato in the trash bin
anns.task_desc: Drop the chilled  slice tomato in the trash bin

high_descs: Walk toward the table then go right until reaching the counter.
Pick up the knife with the yellow handle.
Turn around and walk forward to the table.
Slice up the tomato on the table.
Turn right, go to the counter then turn left to the wall and face the trash bin on the right.
Put the knife inside the trash bin.
Turnaround and go back to spot by the table where it is closest to the refrigerator.
Pick up the middle tomato slice from the table.
Turn around and go stand in front of the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator, put the tomato slice on the same shelf as the potato, close it then take out the tomato slice after several seconds.
Turn right to the table, then right again to the counter, then turn left to the wall and face the trash bin on the right.
Put the tomato slice in the trash bin so that it cannot be seen.
anns.task_desc: Put the knife and a chilled tomato slice in the trash bin.
